?resize=768%2C584&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/28c9d7e6-7322-49ca-870b-70e023c08028.jpg?resize=1024%2C779&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/28c9d7e6-7322-49ca-870b-70e023c08028.jpg?resize=58%2C44&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/28c9d7e6-7322-49ca-870b-70e023c08028.jpg?resize=255%2C194&amp;ssl=1 255w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/28c9d7e6-7322-49ca-870b-70e023c08028.jpg?resize=171%2C130&amp;ssl=1 171w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/28c9d7e6-7322-49ca-870b-70e023c08028.jpg?resize=560%2C426&amp;ssl=1 560w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Ahead of the November 16th Governorship election in Kogi State, Igala Sons in Governor Bello’s Government led by the 45year old Deputy Governor Of Kogi State, His Excellency Chief Edward Unekwuojo Onoja (CIK), Senator Jibrin Isah Echocho, APC members of the National and the State Assemblies from Kogi East, Hon. Commissioners and Special Advisers have gifted the traditional ruler with Royal White sparkling Rolls Royce Phantom. Speaking at the presentation yesterday, the Deputy Governor who holds the traditional title of Olimene of Attah said, “HRM Attah Igala as King Of the 9th Largest Ethnic Nationality in Nigeria in the face of the Igala nation and his appearance must show class,royalty and purity. We give thanks to Governor Yahaya Bello who lifted a lot of progressive minded and passionate leaders in just few years.” <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1279339" src="https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/6441a2c6-5fbf-4c8e-a350-40f4a1e8057b.jpg?resize=640%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="469" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/6441a2c6-5fbf-4c8e-a350-40f4a1e8057b.jpg?w=1114&amp;ssl=1 1114w, https://i2.wp.com